<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>exam on Yafa Xena's blog</title><link>https://www.yafa.moe/tags/exam/</link><description>Recent content in exam on Yafa Xena's blog</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>en</language><lastBuildDate>Tue, 30 Mar 2021 22:42:54 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://www.yafa.moe/tags/exam/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>CKA Docker 基础</title><link>https://www.yafa.moe/post/cka-docker-basic/</link><pubDate>Tue, 30 Mar 2021 22:42:54 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.yafa.moe/post/cka-docker-basic/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="前言">前言&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>目前的运维行业有个趋势就是&lt;a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cloud_native_computing">云原生&lt;/a>，可以看到的趋势就是像是&lt;a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Container_format_(computing)">容器&lt;/a>和&lt;a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Serverless_computing">无服务计算&lt;/a>开始慢慢推行。结合实际工作上有一个趋势那就是上云，为了能够更好的了解其基础我打算从容器入手，像是工作中用到的&lt;a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kubernetes">k8s&lt;/a>和&lt;a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Docker_(software)">docker&lt;/a>之类的，这次打算好好学一学，同时呢也报名了&lt;a href="https://training.linuxfoundation.org/certification/certified-kubernetes-administrator-cka/">CKA&lt;/a>和&lt;a href="https://training.linuxfoundation.org/certification/certified-kubernetes-security-specialist/">CKS&lt;/a>的考试，这里记录一下所学的笔记和实际遇到的问题。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>这篇文章是关于CKA考试中使用到的runtime docker的基础部分。&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>